{"tid":1743577,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑似設立臨時禁飛區   DJI 禁航拍機飛近紅磡理工","createTime":"2019-11-21T09:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:36:20.000Z","uid":58335,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3384551b64a224d0f5f690b3fb2eaa6954db205f","tid":1743577,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"要看清楚大範圍的全局，利用航拍機進行高空拍攝不可少。最近黑衫抗爭者在紅磡理工的事件，加上警察的處理手法均引起全球關注，利用航拍協助報導和了解局勢相當普遍。不過版主就收到網民爆料，懷疑大陸航拍機生產商 DJI 突然於紅磡理工大學附近設置臨時禁飛區。<br />\n<br />\n疑似設立臨時禁飛區   DJI 禁航拍機飛近紅磡理工<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/dc/img/2019-11/20/25863/uniqlo_1_ff8f9adb6e1b362223d21c4d89be2208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fdc%2Fimg%2F2019-11%2F20%2F25863%2Funiqlo_1_ff8f9adb6e1b362223d21c4d89be2208.jpg&h=2d717006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方圍堵理工大學已經來到第 4 日，由於警方的封鎖線伸延至尖沙咀百週年紀念公園和科學館等地，很多媒體希望以高空拍攝配合報導。根據 USP 社媒的報導（下圖），他們的攝影記者嘗試以航拍機飛近理工大學附近，就發現訊號受到干擾。版主收到網民爆料，以 DJI 航拍機飛近紅磡理工會出現無訊號的情況，但其他品牌的航拍機則可以如常運作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/dc/img/2019-11/20/25863/uniqlo_1_20f1082120fe9f14c0de81faba5ee6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fdc%2Fimg%2F2019-11%2F20%2F25863%2Funiqlo_1_20f1082120fe9f14c0de81faba5ee6ad.jpg&h=e29526b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似設立臨時禁飛區   DJI 禁航拍機飛近紅磡理工<br />\n<br />\n報料網民懷疑是大陸航拍品牌 DJI 突然在紅磡理工大學一帶設置禁飛區，阻止傳媒或民間飛近監察。版主嘗試登入 DJI 官方網站了解香港的禁飛區資料，未見理工大學一帶被列入禁飛範圍，不過官網亦提到為配合當局執法和法例需求，DJI 有可能將部份禁飛區資料隱藏。<br />\n<br />\n疑似設立臨時禁飛區   DJI 禁航拍機飛近紅磡理工<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/dc/img/2019-11/20/25863/uniqlo_1_fe5e68c71b6d2b86d1c030a79367a12b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fdc%2Fimg%2F2019-11%2F20%2F25863%2Funiqlo_1_fe5e68c71b6d2b86d1c030a79367a12b.jpg&h=c9010c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總部位於深圳的 DJI 以往亦有設置臨時禁飛區的紀錄，2017 年 7 月國家領導人習近平訪港期間，就有消息指 DJI 在維港兩岸設置臨時禁飛區。當習近平去年 10 月底到廣東考察，深圳突然全市禁飛。版主嘗試聯繫 DJI 有關理工大學附近的禁飛事宜，但暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/dc/talk/315/25863/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fdc%2Ftalk%2F315%2F25863%2F1%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=9726f8ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/dc/talk/315/25863/1/</a>"},{"pid":"696bfb0cdf2c30a72c722b04ad5c39aa0c88c3c3","tid":1743577,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"抵美國佬制裁<br />\n呢單野要俾Solomon知"},{"pid":"2cdbc923c284d5b3ad5b492e363dd02ecfb8f05c","tid":1743577,"uid":51840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"推上 Twitter Reddit"},{"pid":"a97f85f6dfe42d61594db1a13142e9b0a9a77dad","tid":1743577,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70cfa3763cb9f08e5288c8d436b8415a3102a2d9","tid":1743577,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb69083fbd22caf8c628e6a70e8fbba8279e0ac8","tid":1743577,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"Dji<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72906ce2305fdb73cdc3ce580b029e5e96c67a85","tid":1743577,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696bfb0cdf2c30a72c722b04ad5c39aa0c88c3c3","tid":1743577,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"抵美國佬制裁<br />\n呢單野要俾Solomon知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"都已經唔係第一次咁做<br />\n垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e252a44c87a24270958b36715f4b1e8cb580e3d","tid":1743577,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy